{"title":"效率神器 - VSCode的Snippets","date":"2019-05-29T02:14:51.000Z","slug":"vc-snippets","tags":["editor","snippets","vscode"],"categories":["VSCode,Editor"],"updated":"2019-05-29T02:53:13.582Z","content":"<p>写Hexo博客总得在前面加上头信息，然后每次写一篇博客都得打开其他的文件复制，很麻烦。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: 文章标题</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 时间</span><br><span class=\"line\">tags: [标签]</span><br><span class=\"line\">categories: 分类</span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>对，就是每次都需要加上这些东西。然后我就想到了snippet。</p>\n<p>好用的snippet和plugin应该是现代编辑器必须有的功能了吧，毕竟现在这个年代可不像以前，生活节奏这么快，大家每天都在忙碌。</p>\n<p>以前从来没试过自定义snippet，刚刚试了下，感觉到了它的强大之后我打算把VSCode的各种奇淫技巧好好学学了，我真的也就只发挥出了它强大功能的10%。</p>\n<h3 id=\"创建Snippets\">创建Snippets<a href=\"post/vc-snippets#创建Snippets\"></a></h3><p>首先我是一个很不愿意用鼠标的人，我觉得把手移动过去太费劲了，累死累活的。。。</p>\n<p>所以我们<code>Ctrl+Shift+P</code>，输入<code>pcus</code>，应该会定位到一个<code>Preferences: Configure User Snippets</code>，选择它，然后输入<code>new</code>应该就能看见新建Snippets了。</p>\n<p>之后会给你生成一个Json文件，并且注释里面有一个示例，我们可以把它全部删掉了。</p>\n<p>Snippets就是一个Json文件，一个文件里可以定义很多个Snippet，每一个Snippet大概长这个样子：<br><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\"Snippet名\":&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \"scope\": \"Snippet作用范围\",</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \"prefix\": \"Snippet前缀\",</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \"body\": [</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">\"这里就是Snippet被使用后插入的内容\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    ],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \"description\": \"Snippet的介绍\"</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>很简单，因为我们需要使用一个Snippet的时候就是我们在编辑器里输入一些特定的短的前缀，然后选中这个Snippet就会生成想要的东西。</p>\n<p>那么我们开始编写我们的Snippet，我们想要生成Hexo文档的头信息，所以我们这样写：<br><figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">\"Hexo Header\"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"scope\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"markdown\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"prefix\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"!h\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"body\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"---\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"title: $&#123;1:YOURTITLE&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"date: $&#123;CURRENT_YEAR&#125;-$&#123;CURRENT_MONTH&#125;-$&#123;CURRENT_DATE&#125; $&#123;CURRENT_HOUR&#125;:$&#123;CURRENT_MINUTE&#125;:$&#123;CURRENT_SECOND&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"tags: [$&#123;2:TAG&#125;]\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"categories: $&#123;4:CATEGORIES&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"---\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t],</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"description\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"Insert Hexo Header\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>body是一个列表，其中的每一个字符串都是要插入的一行，<code>${var}</code>这种形式则是引用一些变量，也可以直接是<code>$var</code>，我们这里引用了一些VSCode提供的特殊变量。</p>\n<p>关于<code>${1:xxx}</code>这种形式称作占位符，大概就是一个数字+冒号+一段文字，当我们的Snippet被插入时，VSCode会显示这些占位符后面的文字，并将这些占位符中的文字选中，方便直接修改占位符，然后当按下tab时，就会跳转到下一个占位符。</p>\n<p>大概就是这样：</p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"http://prgs9av8q.bkt.clouddn.com/vsc-snp1.gif\" alt=\"演示图片\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>我们引用的变量在VSCode的官方文档里都有介绍，就不一一说明了。可以看这个<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/editor/userdefinedsnippets#_creating-your-own-snippets\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">官方教程</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"其他Snippet\">其他Snippet<a href=\"post/vc-snippets#其他Snippet\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">\"Hexo Header\"</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"scope\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"markdown\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"prefix\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"!h\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"body\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"---\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"title: $&#123;1:YOURTITLE&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"date: $&#123;CURRENT_YEAR&#125;-$&#123;CURRENT_MONTH&#125;-$&#123;CURRENT_DATE&#125; $&#123;CURRENT_HOUR&#125;:$&#123;CURRENT_MINUTE&#125;:$&#123;CURRENT_SECOND&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"tags: [$&#123;2:TAG&#125;]\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"categories: $&#123;4:CATEGORIES&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"---\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t],</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"description\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"Insert Hexo Header\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">\"Java Code\"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"scope\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"markdown\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"prefix\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"`j\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"body\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"```java\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"$1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"```\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t],</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"description\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"Insert Java Code\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">\"Python code\"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"scope\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"markdown\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"prefix\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"`p\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"body\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"```python\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"$1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"```\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t],</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"description\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"Insert Python Code\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attr\">\"Others code\"</span>:&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"scope\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"markdown\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"prefix\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"`c\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"body\"</span>: [</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"```$&#123;1:LANGUAGE&#125;\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"string\">\"```\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t],</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"attr\">\"description\"</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"Insert Code Block\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注意，只有在开启如下选项时，markdown文件中才会出现代码提示。</p>\n<p>在settings.json中设置：<br><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">\"[markdown]\":  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \"editor.quickSuggestions\": true</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","next":{"title":"Future Flash","slug":"sd-futureflash"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/vc-snippets/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"LIL PIG","link":"<a href=\"http://yoursite.com/post/vc-snippets/\" title=\"效率神器 - VSCode的Snippets\">http://yoursite.com/post/vc-snippets/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}